`feedback <https://github.com/shopinvader/odoo-shopinvader/issues/new?body=module:%20shopinvader_locomotive_impersonate%0Aversion:%2014.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**>`_.

